  "texts": [
    "Only in a couple of instances, the response time was longer than 10 seconds, probably due to networking issues.",
    "UCI-ADL is associated with slightly higher response times due to the fact that it involves 60 seconds windows, while MARBLE considered 16 seconds windows.",
    "It is important to note that all the supervised baseline models exhibit significantly faster inference times, processing each window on average in less than one millisecond.",
    "Among them, MLP is the fastest, with an average inference time of 0.000078 (±0.000069) seconds.",
    "DeepConvLSTM follows with 0.000177 (±0.000108) seconds, while BiLSTM is the slowest baseline with an average response time of 0.000356 (±0.000307) seconds."
